  "artwork_generated_url": "",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 13.98,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.98,
      "end": 33.82,
      "text": "영화 속 생생한 영어 표현 배우기"
    },
    {
      "start": 33.82,
      "end": 35.5,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.5,
      "end": 38.28,
      "text": "10월에는 우리가 함께 하고 있는 영화가요"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.28,
      "end": 40.56,
      "text": "It's on the big screen again"
    },
    {
      "start": 40.56,
      "end": 41.84,
      "text": "The secret garden"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.84,
      "end": 43.6,
      "text": "정답입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.6,
      "end": 46.04,
      "text": "It is on the big screen again"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.04,
      "end": 47.88,
      "text": "Yeah, 굿모닝이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.88,
      "end": 49.28,
      "text": "굿모닝입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.28,
      "end": 54.06,
      "text": "우리가 어제 마을사 덕을 좀 받지 않습니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.06,
      "end": 59.3,
      "text": "She was a helper or a sort of servant of Mary"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.3,
      "end": 61.2,
      "text": "Yes, a servant of the whole house"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.2,
      "end": 63.96,
      "text": "And also a life saver"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.96,
      "end": 68.94,
      "text": "She saved the kids while they were trying to sneak out"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.94,
      "end": 70.14,
      "text": "Yeah, 맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.14,
      "end": 72.54,
      "text": "Do you know what her real name is?"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.98,
      "end": 73.86,
      "text": "The actress's name?"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.9,
      "end": 74.2,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.2,
      "end": 77.24,
      "text": "It's the first time for me to see her, I believe"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.24,
      "end": 79.42,
      "text": "So I did not know before today"
    },
    {
      "start": 79.42,
      "end": 82.56,
      "text": "Isis Davis"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.56,
      "end": 85.44,
      "text": "라고 빌리우는 이름인 것 같더라고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.44,
      "end": 86.26,
      "text": "Isis Davis"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.26,
      "end": 88.14,
      "text": "I'm not sure about the pronunciation"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.14,
      "end": 89.14,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 89.14,
      "end": 90.7,
      "text": "Isis 맞을 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 90.7,
      "end": 91.5,
      "text": "Well, Davis"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.5,
      "end": 93.54,
      "text": "That's a city in California"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.54,
      "end": 93.88,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.88,
      "end": 95.86,
      "text": "I graduated from UC Davis"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.86,
      "end": 97.38,
      "text": "Which is a school right there"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.38,
      "end": 97.72,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.72,
      "end": 99.04,
      "text": "Very familiar name"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.04,
      "end": 99.52,
      "text": "그래요"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.52,
      "end": 102.82,
      "text": "But this is the first time for me to encounter this actress"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.82,
      "end": 104.26,
      "text": "저도 마찬가지인데"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.26,
      "end": 107.78,
      "text": "이 비밀의 화원이 영화로 만들어진 이후에"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.78,
      "end": 110.98,
      "text": "She said to be the first black person to play this role"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.98,
      "end": 111.4,
      "text": "Aha"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.4,
      "end": 112.22,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.22,
      "end": 113.88,
      "text": "Before it was a white lady"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.88,
      "end": 114.22,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.22,
      "end": 118.84,
      "text": "그동안에는 계속 백인 여성들이 이 역할을 연기를 했다고 하는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.84,
      "end": 121.6,
      "text": "최초의 흑인으로서 연기를 했대요"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.6,
      "end": 122.12,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.12,
      "end": 123.58,
      "text": "And what else about her?"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.72,
      "end": 125.8,
      "text": "Oh, well, she has appeared in some TV shows"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.8,
      "end": 130.52,
      "text": "Including Casualty, EastEnders, and Silent Witness"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.52,
      "end": 133.4,
      "text": "I have not seen any of them"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.4,
      "end": 133.88,
      "text": "Me either"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.88,
      "end": 136.68,
      "text": "And she was very proud about this role"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.68,
      "end": 139.66,
      "text": "She said, I feel beyond proud"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.66,
      "end": 140.94,
      "text": "Beyond proud"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.94,
      "end": 141.26,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.26,
      "end": 144.76,
      "text": "That I am the first black, mixed-race Martha"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.76,
      "end": 145.84,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.84,
      "end": 148.36,
      "text": "So she has a mixed-racial background"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.36,
      "end": 149.02,
      "text": "Oh, 그러네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.02,
      "end": 150.58,
      "text": "So for there"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.58,
      "end": 151.96,
      "text": "She went on"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.96,
      "end": 154.02,
      "text": "For there now to be a non-white Martha"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.02,
      "end": 156.64,
      "text": "For children who are black, mixed-race"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.64,
      "end": 159.56,
      "text": "They might have seen the films or read the story"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.56,
      "end": 162.46,
      "text": "And not been able to relate to any of the characters"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.46,
      "end": 164.8,
      "text": "They see people that look like them"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.8,
      "end": 166.9,
      "text": "With Martha and Dickon on screen"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.9,
      "end": 168.96,
      "text": "And I think that's really important"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.96,
      "end": 169.94,
      "text": "Yeah, 그래요"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.94,
      "end": 172.48,
      "text": "여태까지는 이 역할을 다 백인들이 했었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.48,
      "end": 176.5,
      "text": "이제는 새로운 시각으로 바라볼 수 있는 계기가 됐잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.5,
      "end": 177.84,
      "text": "Ah, Dickon was also"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.84,
      "end": 179.4,
      "text": "He was a non-white character"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.4,
      "end": 180.18,
      "text": "그러니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.18,
      "end": 182.26,
      "text": "Ah, it's no wonder she's proud of herself"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.26,
      "end": 183.88,
      "text": "She is beyond proud"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.88,
      "end": 184.32,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.32,
      "end": 186.72,
      "text": "That she's the first black Martha"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.72,
      "end": 189.34,
      "text": "네, 일단 오늘 장면 듣고 오겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.34,
      "end": 191.44,
      "text": "When we tried to fix the dog"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.44,
      "end": 192.7,
      "text": "He refused us to"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.7,
      "end": 194.02,
      "text": "Take his legs taken"
    },
    {
      "start": 194.02,
      "end": 195.36,
      "text": "I'll take the arms"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.36,
      "end": 197.96,
      "text": "We can get you in the chair"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.96,
      "end": 199.66,
      "text": "Get you down safely"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.66,
      "end": 201.66,
      "text": "I promise you we won't kill you"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.66,
      "end": 203.48,
      "text": "You can't promise anything of the kind"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.48,
      "end": 204.86,
      "text": "You'll die in this bed"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.86,
      "end": 206.93,
      "text": "And all you'll have seen is the wallpaper"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.93,
      "end": 209.1,
      "text": "Is that really what you want?"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.71,
      "end": 211.49,
      "text": "Well, Mary"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.49,
      "end": 213.43,
      "text": "What a motivational speaker"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.43,
      "end": 214.87,
      "text": "Yeah, 그렇기도 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.87,
      "end": 216.23,
      "text": "또 Colin에 대해서는"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.23,
      "end": 218.21,
      "text": "I think he's a bit stubborn kid"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.21,
      "end": 218.77,
      "text": "Oh, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.77,
      "end": 220.19,
      "text": "They're both stubborn"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.19,
      "end": 222.03,
      "text": "In their own ways"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.03,
      "end": 222.31,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.31,
      "end": 224.41,
      "text": "둘 다 고집이 장난이 아니에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.41,
      "end": 225.09,
      "text": "Oh, yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.09,
      "end": 227.33,
      "text": "It's probably because"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.33,
      "end": 228.59,
      "text": "The door of his mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.59,
      "end": 229.25,
      "text": "To wire the world"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.25,
      "end": 230.15,
      "text": "Hasn't opened yet"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.15,
      "end": 230.75,
      "text": "That's right"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.75,
      "end": 232.19,
      "text": "His heart is closed"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.19,
      "end": 232.53,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.53,
      "end": 233.73,
      "text": "He has many scars"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.73,
      "end": 235.55,
      "text": "And Mary wants to"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.55,
      "end": 236.95,
      "text": "Break him out of his shell"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.95,
      "end": 237.27,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.27,
      "end": 238.55,
      "text": "Come out and see the world"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.55,
      "end": 238.87,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.87,
      "end": 239.61,
      "text": "Come on, Colin"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.61,
      "end": 241.29,
      "text": "You can't spend your whole life"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.29,
      "end": 241.93,
      "text": "In this room"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.93,
      "end": 243.89,
      "text": "이 사촌을 생각하는"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.89,
      "end": 244.87,
      "text": "Mary의 마음이"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.87,
      "end": 246.45,
      "text": "참 고운 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.45,
      "end": 248.33,
      "text": "She's a sweet girl"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.33,
      "end": 248.77,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.77,
      "end": 249.83,
      "text": "She's a sweet girl"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.83,
      "end": 251.39,
      "text": "Behind all that"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.39,
      "end": 251.89,
      "text": "Sassy"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.89,
      "end": 252.85,
      "text": "Rude"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.85,
      "end": 253.93,
      "text": "Exterior"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.93,
      "end": 255.11,
      "text": "보면 볼수록"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.11,
      "end": 255.99,
      "text": "너무 사랑스러운"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.99,
      "end": 257.07,
      "text": "아이인 것 같습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 257.07,
      "end": 257.81,
      "text": "그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 257.81,
      "end": 259.73,
      "text": "어떤 표현들이 들렸죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.13,
      "end": 260.89,
      "text": "Refused"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.89,
      "end": 262.07,
      "text": "네, refused"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.07,
      "end": 263.17,
      "text": "무슨 의미일까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.63,
      "end": 264.39,
      "text": "거절하다"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.39,
      "end": 265.51,
      "text": "라는 동사에"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.51,
      "end": 266.55,
      "text": "이 D가 붙은 거죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.55,
      "end": 267.47,
      "text": "Refused"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.47,
      "end": 269.56,
      "text": "Wallpaper"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.56,
      "end": 270.7,
      "text": "Wallpaper"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.7,
      "end": 272.38,
      "text": "이거 팝송 가사도"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.38,
      "end": 273.12,
      "text": "생각이 납니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.12,
      "end": 274.7,
      "text": "팝송이라기보다는"
    },
    {
      "start": 274.7,
      "end": 275.68,
      "text": "저는 이제"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.68,
      "end": 277.26,
      "text": "Jazz의 제목으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.26,
      "end": 278.24,
      "text": "Wallpaper이라는"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.24,
      "end": 279.28,
      "text": "노래가 생각이 나는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.28,
      "end": 280.48,
      "text": "아, 노래 있군요"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.48,
      "end": 281.4,
      "text": "네, 아무튼"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.4,
      "end": 282.88,
      "text": "이게 무슨 의미냐면"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.88,
      "end": 283.54,
      "text": "Do you have wallpaper?"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.06,
      "end": 284.68,
      "text": "Yeah, sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.68,
      "end": 285.32,
      "text": "In your house?"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.46,
      "end": 286.18,
      "text": "Sure, of course"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.18,
      "end": 286.74,
      "text": "You have wallpaper?"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.22,
      "end": 287.38,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.38,
      "end": 287.82,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.82,
      "end": 289.44,
      "text": "Wallpaper이라는 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.44,
      "end": 290.14,
      "text": "벽지거든요"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.14,
      "end": 291.02,
      "text": "그러면 만약에"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.02,
      "end": 291.62,
      "text": "가사에"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.62,
      "end": 292.96,
      "text": "Wallpaper이라는 게 들리면"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.96,
      "end": 294.14,
      "text": "벽지"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.14,
      "end": 295.34,
      "text": "어, 벽지"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.34,
      "end": 296.44,
      "text": "막 이러면서 부르는 거잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.44,
      "end": 297.16,
      "text": "무슨 의미죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.56,
      "end": 299.7,
      "text": "좀 특이한 것 같네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.7,
      "end": 300.32,
      "text": "그러게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 300.32,
      "end": 302.16,
      "text": "어쨌든 벽지라는"
    },
    {
      "start": 302.16,
      "end": 303.18,
      "text": "의미라는 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 303.18,
      "end": 305.14,
      "text": "What you want"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.14,
      "end": 306.88,
      "text": "What you want"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.88,
      "end": 308.1,
      "text": "의주동"
    },
    {
      "start": 308.1,
      "end": 309.42,
      "text": "어순으로 쓰였어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.42,
      "end": 310.78,
      "text": "뭔가 큰 문장"
    },
    {
      "start": 310.78,
      "end": 311.96,
      "text": "속에 들어있는"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.96,
      "end": 312.92,
      "text": "구조가 되겠죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 312.92,
      "end": 314.08,
